 PolishAnchors_←{
⍝ Checks whether the src=" part of an image definition is an absolute path name.
⍝ If yes: leave it alone.
⍝ If no: add as many "../" as defined by `level`.
     level←⍺
     html←⍵
     src←{⍵↑⍨⍵⍳'"'}'src="'{(⍴⍺)↓⍵↓⍨(⍺⍷⍵)⍳1}html
     f1←'/'=1⍴src
     f2←'\\'≡2⍴src
     f3←':'∊src
     f1∨f2∨f3:html
     'src="'⎕R('&',↑,/level⍴⊂'../')⊣html
 }
